    <briefdescription>
<para>ONNX Gaze Estimation Model using OpenCV DNN (Layer 3 - Native). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements GazeModel to execute forward pass inference on gaze estimation ONNX/OpenVINO networks (e.g. gaze-estimation-adas-0002). Reconciles input crops, head pose sign conventions, and translates output raw direction vectors to GodotGaze space. </para>
